# ⚠️ Limitations

## Limitations

Although the project provides a unique gamified productivity experience, it currently has some limitations:

### 1. Desktop-Only Application
The application currently runs only as a Java desktop application and does not support mobile devices or web platforms.

### 2. Limited Multiplayer Support
The current version focuses on single-user productivity and lacks real-time social or collaborative features.

### 3. Local Storage Dependency
Data is stored locally, which may lead to data loss if files are accidentally deleted or corrupted.

### 4. No Cloud Backup
The application does not currently support online backups or synchronization across devices.

### 5. Basic Security
User authentication and encrypted storage mechanisms are not implemented in the current version.

### 6. Performance Constraints
As the number of tasks and inventory items grows, performance optimization may become necessary.

### 7. Limited AI Automation
The current system relies on manual task management and does not include intelligent task recommendations.

